        <button class="faq-q" data-faq>Is insurance available?</button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Official contract with material liability for goods. All operations are logged in WMS. Warehouse equipped with 24/7 CCTV and security.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script is:inline>
(function(){
  // Form handler for both hero and CTA forms
  function handleForm(formId) {
    var form = document.getElementById(formId);
    if (!form || form.dataset.handled) return;
    form.dataset.handled = '1';
    form.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      var phoneInput = form.querySelector('input[name="phone"]');
      var ph = phoneInput.value.trim();
      var clean = ph.replace(/\D/g, '');
      if (clean.length < 10) {
        phoneInput.style.borderColor = '#e63329';
        phoneInput.focus();
        return;
      }
      var nameInput = form.querySelector('input[name="name"]');
      var nm = nameInput ? nameInput.value.trim() : '';
      if (typeof window.mtpSubmitLead === 'function') {
        window.mtpSubmitLead(ph, location.pathname, nm);
      }
      form.innerHTML = '<p style="color:#fff;font-size:18px;font-weight:500;padding:16px 0">&#10004; Thank you! We will call you back within 15 minutes.</p>';
      setTimeout(function() {
        window.location.href = '/en/thanks/';
      }, 1500);
    });
  }
  handleForm('heroFormSplit');
  handleForm('ctaFormBottom');

  // Warehouse calculator (vanilla JS)
  (function(){
    var wrap = document.getElementById('calcWrap');
    if(!wrap) return;
    function fmt(n){ return Math.round(n).toLocaleString('en-US'); }
    var cSku=document.getElementById('c-sku'), cOrders=document.getElementById('c-orders');
    var radios=wrap.querySelectorAll('input[name="size"]');
    function getSize(){ var v='medium'; radios.forEach(function(r){if(r.checked)v=r.value;}); return v; }
    function update(){
      var sku=parseInt(cSku.value), orders=parseInt(cOrders.value), size=getSize();
      var sf=size==='small'?0.003:size==='medium'?0.008:0.02;
      var ppo=orders<=10?26:orders<=50?23:orders<=100?21:18;
      var sc=Math.round(sku*sf*650), pc=Math.round(orders*22*ppo), tc=sc+pc;
      document.getElementById('r-sku').textContent=fmt(sku);
      document.getElementById('r-orders').textContent=fmt(orders);
      document.getElementById('r-storage').textContent=fmt(sc)+' UAH';
      document.getElementById('r-picking').textContent=fmt(pc)+' UAH';
      document.getElementById('r-total').textContent=fmt(tc)+' UAH';
      wrap.querySelectorAll('.calc-radio').forEach(function(l){l.classList.remove('active');});
      var sel=wrap.querySelector('.calc-radio input[value="'+size+'"]');
      if(sel) sel.parentElement.classList.add('active');
    }
    cSku.addEventListener('input',update);
    cOrders.addEventListener('input',update);
    radios.forEach(function(r){r.addEventListener('change',update);});
    update();
  })();
})();
</script>

<!-- SECTION 8 — SEO TEXT -->
<section class="article-section">
<div class="ctr">
<div class="badge badge-dark">GOOD TO KNOW</div>
<h2>Warehouse Services for Online Stores: How to Choose a Fulfilment Operator</h2>
<div class="article-content">
<h3>What warehouse services for e-commerce really mean</h3>
<p>Warehouse services for online stores are far more than just renting shelf space. They represent a complete fulfilment cycle: inbound receiving and placement, address-based storage in a WMS, order picking in 30 seconds, packing, four daily shipment runs, and returns processing. MTP Group covers all of this across two warehouses near Kyiv — in Boryspil district and Bilohorodka — totalling 3,700 m² of operational space. Over 10 years of experience and 60,000+ shipments per month.</p>
<h3>Why address-based storage makes a difference</h3>
<p>An address-based WMS means every single unit has its own location: aisle, rack, bin. When an order arrives from your CRM, the system automatically builds the picker's route. Picking takes 30 seconds. Stock levels are available online 24/7 through your personal dashboard. FEFO control automatically tracks expiry dates for cosmetics and supplements. Use our <a href="/en/calculator/" style="color:#e63329;font-weight:500">calculator</a> to estimate your monthly cost.</p>
<h3>When it's time to outsource your warehouse</h3>
<p>The tipping point is around 30–50 orders per day. Below that threshold, self-fulfilment is manageable. But once your store crosses 30 orders, in-house logistics starts to slow growth — you need a warehouse worker, storage space, packing supplies, and a backup generator. MTP Group takes care of the entire infrastructure. Storage from 650 UAH/m³/month, picking from 18 UAH per shipment. Read <a href="/en/recalls/" style="color:#e63329;font-weight:500">client reviews</a> from merchants who have already made the switch.</p>
<h3>Uninterrupted operations during power outages</h3>
<p>MTP Group warehouses are equipped with 3 generators and Starlink internet. Since 2022, there has not been a single missed shipment due to a power cut. WMS and picker terminals operate in offline mode. For e-commerce this is critical — your customers cannot wait for the lights to come back on. See the <a href="/en/services/" style="color:#e63329;font-weight:500">full list of services</a> we provide.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

</Base>

<style>
/* ==========================================
   SECTION 1 — HERO SPLIT-SCREEN
   ========================================== */
.sp-hero {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  min-height: 100vh;
  background: var(--black);
  color: var(--white);
}
.sp-hero-video {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.sp-hero-video video {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  display: block;
}
.sp-hero-form-side {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 80px 48px 60px;
}
.sp-hero-inner {
  max-width: 520px;
  width: 100%;
}
.sp-hero-inner h1 {
  font-family: var(--fd);
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 48px);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.05;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.sp-hero-sub {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.65);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.sp-hero-form {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
}
.sp-hero-form input {
  padding: 14px 18px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
  border-radius: 6px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-family: var(--fb);
  outline: none;
  transition: border-color .2s;
}
.sp-hero-form input::placeholder {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.3);
}
.sp-hero-form input:focus {
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
}
.sp-hero-form button {
  padding: 16px 24px;
  background: var(--red);
  color: #fff;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: var(--fb);
  transition: background .3s;
}
.sp-hero-form button:hover {
  background: #c42b22;
}
.sp-hero-note {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.35);
  margin-top: 14px;
}
.sp-hero-phone {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 10px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.7);
  transition: color .2s;
}
.sp-hero-phone:hover {
  color: #fff;
}

/* Mobile hero: video becomes background, form overlays */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .sp-hero {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    min-height: auto;
    position: relative;
  }
  .sp-hero-video {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .sp-hero-video video {
    opacity: .2;
  }
  .sp-hero-form-side {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 120px 24px 60px;
  }
  .sp-hero-inner h1 {
    font-size: clamp(26px, 7vw, 36px);
  }
}

/* ==========================================
   SECTION 2 — TIMELINE
   ========================================== */
.tl-section {
  padding: 100px 0;
  background: var(--white);
}
.tl-track {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-top: 48px;
}
.tl-line {
  position: absolute;
  top: 14px;
  left: 14px;
  right: 14px;
  height: 3px;
  background: #e0e0e0;
}
.tl-line::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--red);
  transform-origin: left;
}
.tl-step {
  flex: 1;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  text-align: center;
}
.tl-dot {
  width: 30px;
  height: 30px;
  background: var(--red);
  border: 4px solid #fff;
  border-radius: 50%;
  margin: 0 auto 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--red);
}
.tl-content h3 {
  font-family: var(--fd);
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.tl-content p {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.6;
  max-width: 200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Mobile: vertical timeline */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .tl-track {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    padding-left: 30px;
  }
  .tl-line {
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 14px;
    right: auto;
    width: 3px;
    height: auto;
  }
  .tl-step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 20px;
    text-align: left;
    padding-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .tl-dot {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
    left: -30px;
  }
  .tl-content {
    padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .tl-content p {
    max-width: none;
    margin: 0;
  }
